Text: Gulfstream OperatorsMr Lay Is your Gulfstream going in for major maintenance If your answer is yes you are possibly thinking charter to fill the gap Well we have an idea Dry lease our clients GII SP for a period of six to months This lowtime aircraft is ready to go to work for you next week Give us a call at It will be a pleasure to hear from you Weldon Riker President WRIKERvcf
